title: PM suggests Boeing provide incentives to Việt Nam’s airline industry
description: Prime Minister Phạm Minh Chính called on Boeing to offer incentives to Vietnam, at his reception for Brendan Nelson, Vice President of the Boeing Company and President of Boeing International, in Hà Nội on Friday.
